dFile = File(...)):\n54|    \"\"\"上传文件，返回可访问的 URL\n55|\n56|    Returns:\n57|        {\"url\": \"http://localhost:8000/uploads/xxx.jpg\",\n58|         \"file_type\": \"image\"|\"doc\",\n59|         \"filename\": \"xxx.jpg\",\n60|         \"size\": 12345}", "total_lines": 101, "offset": 1, "limit": 60}, "duration_ms": 6}
